---
title: Sheet Pan Chicken Tikka with Buttery Naan
description: Harness the power of your oven to emulate a tandoor tonight! Spiced chicken and veggies are roasted together to make cleanup a breeze, then covered in an aromatic tikka sauce. A cool cilantro yogurt on top complements all those delicious flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-tikka-sur-une-seule-plaque-a-cuisson-69fe2e49.jpg
